    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552500/extras/c168393b120f22bc696110e72a859f17.avif?t=1764008361\" width=748 height=938 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552500/extras/80b0d8043c2641ed091ad08601d5057b.poster.avif?t=1764008361\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552500/extras/80b0d8043c2641ed091ad08601d5057b.webm?t=1764008361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552500/extras/80b0d8043c2641ed091ad08601d5057b.mp4?t=1764008361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《鼠疫》回来了——比之前所有版本都更黑暗、更血腥、更刺激！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《战锤：鼠疫2》是广受好评的《鼠疫》续作。是时候重返这款激烈的第一人称合作屠杀游戏了。这款血糊淋剌的杀戮游戏将背景设定在饱受战乱纷扰的《战锤奇幻世界》终焉之时期间，拥有极具创新性的近战手感。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的五名英雄已然回归，准备抵御更大的威胁——残暴的混沌大军与蜂拥的斯卡文鼠人部落的合力进攻。准备迎接您从未面临过的挑战、让自己的队伍在无止境的杀戮中尽可能地活下来吧。15种不同的职业和各类天赋树任你选择、自定义军火库来搭配您的游戏方式、打通无数扣人心弦的关卡，在全新的英雄事迹系统里挑战自己。胜负之别就在于您与队友的表现。您若倒地，帝国也将陨落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t残酷的4人合作游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t5个英雄</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t15个职业</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t15条天赋树</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t20+种敌人类型</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t50+种不同的武器类型</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t大量扣人心弦的关卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t英雄事迹系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t被动与主动职业技能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t英雄独占装备获取系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t支持Mod（仅限PC）[/IMG]</p>",
